1
00:00:00,387 --> 00:00:08,487
<i>Yeah, turn your sadness into kindness,</i>
<i>your uniqueness into strength</i>

2
00:00:08,662 --> 00:00:16,899
<i>Even if you get lost, let's start walking</i>

3
00:00:17,137 --> 00:00:19,128
<i>One more time</i>

4
00:00:22,142 --> 00:00:25,908
<i>Are you really happy</i>

5
00:00:25,979 --> 00:00:29,346
<i>when you're always meeting</i>
<i>to someone's expectations?</i>

6
00:00:29,549 --> 00:00:33,110
<i>Even if you change to</i>
<i>who you really wanna be</i>

7
00:00:33,486 --> 00:00:36,853
<i>Will you always have a great smile?</i>

8
00:00:36,923 --> 00:00:44,352
<i>Dreaming of only "the beginning,"</i>
<i>I wake up</i>

9
00:00:44,431 --> 00:00:53,567
<i>and someday, I'll live on my own.</i>

10
00:00:53,640 --> 00:01:01,672
<i>Yes, precious things are never in shape</i>

11
00:01:01,915 --> 00:01:08,753
<i>You never know what it is</i>
<i>when you get it or lose it</i>

12
00:01:08,822 --> 00:01:16,888
<i>Yeah, turn your sadness into kindness,</i>
<i>your uniqueness into strength</i>

13
00:01:17,197 --> 00:01:25,662
<i>Even if you get lost,</i>
<i>let's start walking</i>

14
00:01:25,739 --> 00:01:27,764
<i>One more time</i>

15
00:01:35,593 --> 00:01:37,288
Hey! Open up!

16
00:01:39,297 --> 00:01:39,888
Huh?

17
00:01:39,964 --> 00:01:41,955
What's all this noise at this hour?

18
00:01:42,200 --> 00:01:46,193
Idiots! I told you not to let
your eyes off him, didn't I?

19
00:01:53,978 --> 00:01:55,969
Could Gaara have...?

20
00:01:56,047 --> 00:01:57,571
Where on earth did he go?

21
00:02:03,955 --> 00:02:07,083
<i>I hope nothing bad happens, but...</i>

22
00:02:07,792 --> 00:02:13,697
<i>Hospital Beseiged.</i>
<i>The Evil Hand Revealed!</i>

23
00:02:41,492 --> 00:02:45,326
Wow, he's sound asleep...
I wonder if he's dead?

24
00:03:07,585 --> 00:03:10,179
If that's for Sasuke,
he's not back yet.

25
00:03:13,824 --> 00:03:15,018
Hmm.

26
00:03:16,127 --> 00:03:17,116
Ino...

27
00:03:19,797 --> 00:03:22,698
I'm way ahead of you on
Sasuke information.

28
00:03:24,068 --> 00:03:26,935
Missed your chance on that one,
eh, Billboard Brow?

29
00:03:27,405 --> 00:03:30,772
No! This is for Lee!

30
00:03:31,509 --> 00:03:32,339
Huh?

31
00:03:32,977 --> 00:03:35,537
The one from before should
be wilted by now too...

32
00:03:39,116 --> 00:03:40,140
Oh.

33
00:03:40,217 --> 00:03:42,447
<i>Lee! Stop it!</i>

34
00:03:42,520 --> 00:03:44,613
<i>191...</i>

35
00:03:45,022 --> 00:03:46,421
<i>Don't touch me!</i>

36
00:03:46,791 --> 00:03:50,056
<i>I'm...not...done yet...</i>

37
00:03:50,595 --> 00:03:51,425
Here.

38
00:03:53,431 --> 00:03:54,261
Thanks.

39
00:03:55,766 --> 00:03:58,098
I hope Lee's better.

40
00:03:58,502 --> 00:03:59,298
Yeah.

41
00:04:22,660 --> 00:04:23,627
Huh?

42
00:04:24,862 --> 00:04:25,988
What the...?

43
00:04:26,797 --> 00:04:31,393
Oh man, it's all clogged up.
What a drag...

44
00:04:37,274 --> 00:04:38,241
Yo!

45
00:04:38,743 --> 00:04:40,370
You finally woke up, eh?

46
00:04:41,379 --> 00:04:43,745
Where... am I?

47
00:04:43,948 --> 00:04:44,972
In the hospital!

48
00:04:45,049 --> 00:04:48,416
They told me that you've been
sound asleep for 3 days and 3 nights!

49
00:04:49,253 --> 00:04:50,515
Three days...

50
00:04:51,722 --> 00:04:53,622
Three days and three nights?!

51
00:04:54,692 --> 00:04:56,319
W-What?

52
00:04:56,794 --> 00:04:59,160
Shikamaru! When does
the final competition start?

53
00:04:59,230 --> 00:05:00,356
T-Tomorrow.

54
00:05:00,431 --> 00:05:01,830
What?!

55
00:05:02,800 --> 00:05:05,530
Why didn't you wake me
up earlier!

56
00:05:05,603 --> 00:05:08,970
I can't be just snoozing through
in a place like this!

57
00:05:09,140 --> 00:05:10,505
And what about Pervy Sage?

58
00:05:10,574 --> 00:05:12,269
Where's Pervy Sage?!

59
00:05:12,476 --> 00:05:14,501
I've got to have him watch
over my training.

60
00:05:14,578 --> 00:05:16,739
Huh? What are you talking about,
all of a sudden?

61
00:05:16,814 --> 00:05:18,543
I don't know what's got into you.

62
00:05:19,784 --> 00:05:22,048
Huh? My clothes are missing

63
00:05:22,119 --> 00:05:24,087
Where are they?
Where, where?

64
00:05:24,488 --> 00:05:26,979
- Sleeping away like you're in a coma,
- Gone!

65
00:05:27,058 --> 00:05:28,889
- Then running around out of control.
- Where're my clothes?!

66
00:05:29,760 --> 00:05:31,159
Settle down a little!

67
00:05:32,997 --> 00:05:35,625
You know what?
It isn't gonna make a difference

68
00:05:35,700 --> 00:05:37,258
if you rush around
one day beforehand.

69
00:05:37,334 --> 00:05:39,302
Resting is training, too, you know...

70
00:05:39,837 --> 00:05:42,032
Huh? Hey... Naruto.

71
00:05:43,074 --> 00:05:44,234
What in the world
is going on?

72
00:05:45,409 --> 00:05:47,639
I'm... so... hungry...

73
00:05:47,845 --> 00:05:50,837
Don't keep scaring me like that...

74
00:05:50,981 --> 00:05:52,278
Oh yeah.

75
00:05:57,521 --> 00:05:58,988
It's such a drag but...

76
00:05:59,056 --> 00:06:01,684
I bought this fruit basket as
a get well present for Choji.

77
00:06:01,892 --> 00:06:03,723
But the doctor said he couldn't have it.

78
00:06:03,794 --> 00:06:05,091
So let's eat it together.

79
00:06:05,496 --> 00:06:08,590
Choji? Is he that sick?

80
00:06:08,999 --> 00:06:10,489
No, no, don't be fooled.

81
00:06:10,701 --> 00:06:15,536
He got sick from eating
too much BBQ.

82
00:06:17,308 --> 00:06:18,798
That's just like him!

83
00:06:18,943 --> 00:06:22,709
Yeah well, and neither of you are the type
to have female visitors.

84
00:06:23,013 --> 00:06:23,877
So here...

85
00:06:25,816 --> 00:06:27,113
Looks good.

86
00:06:29,653 --> 00:06:31,211
W-What is it?

87
00:06:32,723 --> 00:06:35,590
Since Choji can't have any,
let's eat in front of him.

88
00:06:36,160 --> 00:06:38,321
What a drag this guy is!

89
00:06:39,864 --> 00:06:40,694
Huh?

90
00:06:43,134 --> 00:06:44,294
No one's here.

91
00:06:49,406 --> 00:06:50,430
Out to lunch?

92
00:06:52,810 --> 00:06:53,936
Oh well...

93
00:07:03,420 --> 00:07:04,387
Okay!

94
00:07:05,790 --> 00:07:06,552
Hmm?

95
00:08:14,859 --> 00:08:18,022
Lee, I'm putting the
flowers here, okay?

96
00:08:31,475 --> 00:08:33,204
I'm still hungry!

97
00:08:47,291 --> 00:08:50,522
Are you harassing me, Shikamaru?

98
00:09:11,482 --> 00:09:12,779
Oh yeah.

99
00:09:38,342 --> 00:09:40,503
<i>Why...save him?</i>

100
00:09:42,346 --> 00:09:46,874
<i>He's an important subordinate</i>
<i>whom I care for.</i>

101
00:10:48,145 --> 00:10:50,875
My body... isn't moving.

102
00:10:51,516 --> 00:10:53,313
You jerk!

103
00:10:55,987 --> 00:10:58,854
What the hell do you think
you're doing?!

104
00:11:00,458 --> 00:11:02,153
Hey Naruto...

105
00:11:02,660 --> 00:11:07,757
During Shadow Possession Jutsu,
it's moving me too! Okay?!

106
00:11:08,733 --> 00:11:10,064
Sorry! Shikamaru.

107
00:11:16,140 --> 00:11:18,665
What the hell were you
trying to do?

108
00:11:20,811 --> 00:11:22,938
Choji, are you better?

109
00:11:23,247 --> 00:11:24,714
Oh, Ino!

110
00:11:29,887 --> 00:11:32,048
<i>All right! The age of</i>
<i>the chubby has arrived!</i>

111
00:11:45,002 --> 00:11:48,130
What were you trying to do
to Bushy Brow here?!

112
00:11:50,308 --> 00:11:51,935
I was trying to kill him.

113
00:11:52,343 --> 00:11:53,207
What?!

114
00:11:53,978 --> 00:11:56,242
<i>How can he be so calm?</i>

115
00:11:56,847 --> 00:12:00,783
<i>Especially when he is not able to</i>
<i>move with my Shadow Possession Jutsu...</i>

116
00:12:02,019 --> 00:12:04,351
Why'd you have to do something
like that?

117
00:12:04,989 --> 00:12:07,253
You beat him in the match, right?

118
00:12:07,792 --> 00:12:10,989
Do you have a personal grudge
against him or something?

119
00:12:11,796 --> 00:12:13,457
I don't have anything like that.

120
00:12:15,132 --> 00:12:18,727
I just wanted to kill him, that's it.

121
00:12:18,803 --> 00:12:22,068
How can you say something
so selfish, you bastard?!

122
00:12:22,406 --> 00:12:25,534
You... you had a lousy upbringing,
didn't you?

123
00:12:25,910 --> 00:12:27,844
All you care about is yourself.

124
00:12:28,746 --> 00:12:32,807
<i>Or there's something weird about him.</i>
<i>It gives me the chills!</i>

125
00:12:33,284 --> 00:12:37,084
<i>If he tries anything, it'll be too much</i>
<i>of a burden for me and Naruto...</i>

126
00:12:37,555 --> 00:12:40,353
<i>What the heck should we do?</i>

127
00:12:41,125 --> 00:12:44,288
If you get in my way,
I'll kill you both too.

128
00:12:44,562 --> 00:12:47,258
What?! Go ahead, if you can!

129
00:12:47,331 --> 00:12:48,730
Hey Naruto, hold on!

130
00:12:50,468 --> 00:12:53,028
<i>Should I try to scare him with a bluff?</i>

131
00:12:54,271 --> 00:12:57,672
I know you're strong from seeing you
in the competition with him...

132
00:12:58,142 --> 00:13:02,579
But... we can keep up with you.

133
00:13:03,280 --> 00:13:06,943
We didn't show you our best skills
in the preliminaries.

134
00:13:07,752 --> 00:13:09,310
And it's two against one!

135
00:13:09,687 --> 00:13:11,484
You're the one who's at a disadvantage.

136
00:13:11,789 --> 00:13:15,919
If you're smart, you'll do what
I tell you and just get lost.

137
00:13:16,694 --> 00:13:20,596
I'll say it again...
if you get in my way...

138
00:13:20,965 --> 00:13:21,727
I'll kill you.

139
00:13:22,900 --> 00:13:24,128
<i>Where the heck do you get off...?!</i>

140
00:13:24,735 --> 00:13:27,101
There's no way in hell
I'll let you do that!

141
00:13:27,405 --> 00:13:29,703
I've been telling you
to back off, haven't I?

142
00:13:30,041 --> 00:13:33,477
This guy has the strength of a monster.
You get it, don't you?

143
00:13:34,412 --> 00:13:39,440
I have a real monster in me!
I'm not going to lose to this guy!

144
00:13:50,494 --> 00:13:51,461
Huh?

145
00:13:51,929 --> 00:13:54,454
I heard Naruto was here too,
so I came to see, but...

146
00:13:55,800 --> 00:13:57,631
What a mess...

147
00:13:59,103 --> 00:14:00,832
Well, I guess this means he's okay.

148
00:14:01,772 --> 00:14:02,830
Huh?

149
00:14:07,011 --> 00:14:09,912
What's worth making him mad,
you idiot!

150
00:14:15,886 --> 00:14:17,183
A monster, huh...?

151
00:14:19,256 --> 00:14:21,383
Me too, actually.

152
00:14:23,194 --> 00:14:27,893
It's just like you said.
I had a terrible upbringing.

153
00:14:28,399 --> 00:14:29,889
When I came into this world,

154
00:14:29,967 --> 00:14:32,697
I took the life of the woman
some might call my mother.

155
00:14:33,370 --> 00:14:35,736
So that I could become
the strongest Shinobi...

156
00:14:35,806 --> 00:14:38,400
my father brought his
Ninjutsu upon me,

157
00:14:38,476 --> 00:14:40,706
and so I became possessed
by a Sand Spirit.

158
00:14:41,712 --> 00:14:44,010
I was born a monster.

159
00:14:46,016 --> 00:14:47,506
<i>A Sand Spirit?</i>

160
00:14:48,319 --> 00:14:51,220
It's called Shukaku, the living wraith of
an old monk

161
00:14:51,288 --> 00:14:54,849
from Village Hidden in the Sand
who was sealed inside the tea caldron.

162
00:14:57,628 --> 00:14:59,755
It must be a type of
cacodemon possession Jutsu,

163
00:14:59,830 --> 00:15:01,388
performed to a baby before it is born.

164
00:15:01,465 --> 00:15:04,525
To go that far...
they must have been totally nuts.

165
00:15:07,972 --> 00:15:12,341
<i>Is it possible...that there could be</i>
<i>something inside him too?</i>

166
00:15:16,447 --> 00:15:20,679
What a thing for a parent to be doing!
Such a twisted kind of love.

167
00:15:21,118 --> 00:15:22,551
Love?

168
00:15:22,820 --> 00:15:25,516
Don't measure me by your standards.

169
00:15:27,625 --> 00:15:28,592
Family, huh...

170
00:15:28,959 --> 00:15:33,453
Let me tell you what kind of ties
I have to my family.

171
00:15:34,098 --> 00:15:36,692
They're ties of hatred,
ties of murderous intent...

172
00:15:36,767 --> 00:15:38,667
My family's just lumps of flesh.

173
00:15:40,237 --> 00:15:42,899
Nourished with the life of my mother,

174
00:15:43,207 --> 00:15:46,335
I was crafted as the
ultimate masterpiece of the village...

175
00:15:47,011 --> 00:15:48,911
The Kazekage's child.

176
00:15:49,613 --> 00:15:52,639
I was taught by my father
the innermost secrets of the Shinobi...

177
00:15:52,983 --> 00:15:56,350
spoiled, over protected,
and left on my own.

178
00:15:57,354 --> 00:15:59,720
And I thought that was love...

179
00:16:03,227 --> 00:16:05,525
Until that incident happened.

180
00:16:06,764 --> 00:16:08,026
That incident...?!

181
00:16:11,402 --> 00:16:14,030
What are you talking about?

182
00:16:18,409 --> 00:16:21,071
Just what happened?!

183
00:16:24,648 --> 00:16:27,879
In the six years since the time
when I was 6 years old...

184
00:16:27,952 --> 00:16:31,581
My real father has tried to assassinate me
more times than I can count!

185
00:16:35,459 --> 00:16:38,553
But I thought you just said that
your father spoiled you...

186
00:16:39,296 --> 00:16:40,388
What's going on here?

187
00:16:46,537 --> 00:16:50,735
Those who are too strong are
apt to become feared.

188
00:16:51,508 --> 00:16:54,841
Born through the Jutsu,
my mind was unstable...

189
00:16:55,246 --> 00:16:57,180
I guess the idiots in my village

190
00:16:57,248 --> 00:17:00,217
finally realized that
I had emotional problems...

191
00:17:01,452 --> 00:17:03,443
For my father, Kazekage

192
00:17:03,520 --> 00:17:06,387
at the same time I was
the ultimate weapon for the village

193
00:17:06,457 --> 00:17:09,187
I was also a dangerous,
fearsome presence.

194
00:17:09,693 --> 00:17:14,926
It seems I was labeled a dangerous figure
as soon as I turned six.

195
00:17:15,566 --> 00:17:20,196
And I was treated politely simply because
I was feared.

196
00:17:20,671 --> 00:17:24,573
To them, now I'm just a relic of the past
that they want to see disappear.

197
00:17:26,243 --> 00:17:30,077
So what did I have in this life,
why did I keep living?

198
00:17:30,981 --> 00:17:33,643
When I asked myself that,
I couldn't find the answer.

199
00:17:34,752 --> 00:17:38,984
But, as long as you're alive,
you need a reason...

200
00:17:39,623 --> 00:17:41,989
If you don't have one,
it's just the same as being dead.

201
00:17:42,192 --> 00:17:44,319
What's this guy saying?

202
00:17:47,164 --> 00:17:49,962
<i>I...can understand that...</i>

203
00:17:50,734 --> 00:17:54,033
<i>He...is the same as me.</i>

204
00:17:54,939 --> 00:17:57,100
So this is the answer I came to...

205
00:17:57,775 --> 00:18:01,768
I am living in order to kill
human beings other than myself.

206
00:18:02,313 --> 00:18:05,680
After living in the fear of never knowing
when I might be murdered,

207
00:18:05,749 --> 00:18:07,717
finally I became calm.

208
00:18:08,886 --> 00:18:15,450
By killing assassins, I finally
comprehended the reason why I live...

209
00:18:16,226 --> 00:18:19,889
I live fighting for only myself
and loving myself...

210
00:18:20,698 --> 00:18:23,997
And if I see that all other people
in this world exist

211
00:18:24,134 --> 00:18:25,999
only to make me realize that,

212
00:18:26,070 --> 00:18:28,368
there could be no world
more wonderful.

213
00:18:29,106 --> 00:18:32,667
And as long as there are
others to kill

214
00:18:32,743 --> 00:18:36,577
who can make me feel
this happiness to be alive,

215
00:18:37,982 --> 00:18:40,177
I will never disappear.

216
00:18:40,451 --> 00:18:42,316
<i>W-What's this freak talking about...?</i>

217
00:18:42,753 --> 00:18:44,152
<i>He's real gone!</i>

218
00:18:44,521 --> 00:18:46,352
<i>I was also alone...</i>

219
00:18:46,924 --> 00:18:50,052
<i>And suffered 'cause</i>
<i>I didn't know why I was alive...</i>

220
00:18:50,427 --> 00:18:54,420
<i>But Iruka Sensei recognized me</i>
<i>for who I was...</i>

221
00:18:54,498 --> 00:18:57,956
<i>and that was the first time</i>
<i>I realized why I lived...</i>

222
00:18:58,635 --> 00:19:03,129
<i>But this guy...</i>
<i>this guy grew up alone.</i>

223
00:19:03,607 --> 00:19:07,907
<i>And he ony feels alive</i>
<i>when he kills other people.</i>

224
00:19:12,049 --> 00:19:13,812
<i>H-How can there be someone like this?</i>

225
00:19:18,188 --> 00:19:21,351
<i>The worlds we live in</i>
<i>are too different...!</i>

226
00:19:24,762 --> 00:19:28,129
<i>There's no way...</i>
<i>that I can beat a guy like this!</i>

227
00:19:30,401 --> 00:19:32,835
W-What's wrong, Naruto?

228
00:19:40,477 --> 00:19:44,971
<i>What? Shadow Possession Jutsu should</i>
<i>have stopped him from moving, but...</i>

229
00:19:51,055 --> 00:19:51,817
Naruto!

230
00:19:52,689 --> 00:19:54,213
Naruto! Hey, get yourself together!

231
00:19:54,658 --> 00:19:56,285
What a drag this guy is!

232
00:19:56,593 --> 00:19:57,651
Naruto!

233
00:19:58,228 --> 00:20:00,458
Now, let me feel it...!

234
00:20:02,966 --> 00:20:03,830
Oh no!

235
00:20:04,601 --> 00:20:05,397
Stop right there!

236
00:20:07,037 --> 00:20:08,504
Tomorrow's the final round!

237
00:20:08,639 --> 00:20:10,664
There's no need to rush like this!

238
00:20:11,175 --> 00:20:13,905
Or do you just want to
stay here starting today?

239
00:20:15,546 --> 00:20:16,945
<i>Don't leave me alone!</i>

240
00:20:17,381 --> 00:20:20,646
<i>I'm not bleeding, but</i>
<i>it hurts a lot right here.</i>

241
00:20:24,555 --> 00:20:27,718
<i>What...am I?!</i>

242
